		<title>Episode 200 – One Geek Moves On</title>
		<link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/AirplaneGeeksPodcast/~3/gRLESIVMbfs/</link>
		<comments>http://www.airplanegeeks.com/2012/06/05/episode-200-one-geek-moves-on/#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Wed, 06 Jun 2012 01:05:32 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator>thegeeks@airplanegeeks.com (Airplane Geeks)</dc:creator>
