		<item>
		<title>Episode 198 – Kip Hawley on the TSA</title>
		<link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/AirplaneGeeksPodcast/~3/vqE3Cc0TaOo/</link>
		<comments>http://www.airplanegeeks.com/2012/05/22/episode-198-kip-hawley-on-the-tsa/#comments</comments>
