		<title>Episode 182 – Alan Epstein and the Geared Turbofan Engine</title>
		<link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/AirplaneGeeksPodcast/~3/nBaERy4kHjM/</link>
		<comments>http://www.airplanegeeks.com/2012/01/24/episode-182-alan-epstein-and-the-geared-turbofan-engine/#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Wed, 25 Jan 2012 01:11:59 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator>thegeeks@airplanegeeks.com (Airplane Geeks)</dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Episodes]]></category>
